Key Match Events: South Africa lost to Netherlands by 13 runs, crashing out of the T20 World Cup
Colin Ackermann's late-hitting led Netherlands to a strong total
Post-Match Reflections: South Africa's elimination was a significant moment in the tournament
The match marked the end of their journey in the T20 World Cup 2022
Miscellaneous Highlights: The loss meant India qualified for the semi-finals
The next match between Pakistan and Bangladesh will decide the second semi-finalist from Group 2
